01:24:51.310 --> 01:24:54.109
<i>And you can't tell
anyone about me.</i>

01:24:54.111 --> 01:24:56.614
<i>How much is that gonna cut you
off from your family?</i>

01:24:58.182 --> 01:25:01.086
<i>How much is that gonna cut you
