Like a radio flipping
from station to station.

01:27:02.339 --> 01:27:04.142
Hard to get control of.

01:27:05.909 --> 01:27:07.078
What else?

01:27:08.046 --> 01:27:09.481
Um...

01:27:11.281 --> 01:27:12.484
I'm thinking.

