01:27:44.515 --> 01:27:45.684
<i>Far away.</i>

01:27:47.318 --> 01:27:48.486
<i>New York.</i>

01:27:49.887 --> 01:27:51.523
<i>Chicago, if I can get there.</i>

01:27:53.792 --> 01:27:56.192
<i>Just some big, dense city</i>

